{"tid":1869311,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【防疫注意】女子全身噴灑大量酒精消毒 一入廚房搶火爆燃 臉手嚴重燒傷","createTime":"2020-02-08T06:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T11:42:08.000Z","uid":2889,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c736f488ba56fa05717f540b7300931d3fab1514","tid":1869311,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:15:48.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎肆虐，不少市民為了加強消毒，大量使用含有酒精的清潔用品，但是也要注意安全。近日中國一名女士在身上噴灑過量酒精消毒後，回到廚房時引起搶火爆炸，嚴重受傷。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中國新聞媒體報導，事發於2月5日，合肥一名女士使用酒精噴霧為自己消毒，噴灑全身後相隔不夠2分鐘，她便再入廚房查看餸菜情況，怎料還未靠近爐頭，揮發的酒精突然閃燃搶火，引發爆炸，外露部位如臉部、手部等嚴重燒傷，需要留院繼續治理。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源地址:<a href=\"http://www.ohpama.com/503797/24parent/%e5%a5%b3%e5%ad%90%e5%85%a8%e8%ba%ab%e5%99%b4%e7%81%91%e5%a4%a7%e9%87%8f%e9%85%92%e7%b2%be%e6%b6%88%e6%af%92/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohpama.com%2F503797%2F24parent%2F%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e5%25ad%2590%25e5%2585%25a8%25e8%25ba%25ab%25e5%2599%25b4%25e7%2581%2591%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e9%2587%258f%25e9%2585%2592%25e7%25b2%25be%25e6%25b6%2588%25e6%25af%2592%2F&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=51e30c90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ohpama.com/503797/24parent/%e5%a5%b3%e5%ad%90%e5%85%a8%e8%ba%ab%e5%99%b4%e7%81%91%e5%a4%a7%e9%87%8f%e9%85%92%e7%b2%be%e6%b6%88%e6%af%92/</a><br />\n<br />\nOh!爸媽親子新聞 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320555dbb2648a564e1c8d468a440825a96b55ec","tid":1869311,"uid":34010,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:17:28.000Z","msg":"成功消毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7da20dd81d0c8aaec4c0d62957bab805f4dbd5","tid":1869311,"uid":65911,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:18:28.000Z","msg":"無常識真係好恐怖